title: Moonlight Runner v1.1.0 [PD]
description:
Get ready to blast off on an epic Running journey with Moon Light Runner
Collect the golden bugs , and avoid enemies to reach to your final destination. 
And enjoy the Spanish guitar :)

Moon Light Runner has got what you need.

Tap to jump and collect as many as possible of the golden bugs and try to discover the hidden paths for a higher score.
A NEW LEVEL will be added SOON; so stay tuned.

**********UPDATE***********

A NEW amazing level "LEVEL 6" has been added and unlocked.
Added support for high resolution devices.
A new type of game play hope you will enjoy it.
